<section class="section resume-section" id="resume" aria-labelledby="resume-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="resume-inner card">
      <div class="resume-text">
        <h2 class="section-title" id="resume-heading" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Резюме</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--c-text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-sm);max-width:480px;">
          Полное резюме доступно по запросу. Напишите в Telegram или на email — отвечаю в течение дня.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-actions">
        <a
          href="https://t.me/Kost_Pop"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn--primary"
          aria-label="Запросить резюме в Telegram"
        >
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg>
          Запросить резюме
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .resume-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-bg-card) 0%, rgba(59,130,246,0.04) 100%);
  }

  @media (max-width: 580px) {
    .resume-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
